# Take screenshots
##copy screenshot to clipboard from current screen
Print
  flameshot screen -c

##save and copy screenshot from current screen
ctrl + Print
  flameshot screen -c -p ~/media/pics/screen/

##copy rectangle select to clipboard
shift + Print
  flameshot gui -c

##save and copy rectangle select from current screen
ctrl + shift + Print
  flameshot gui -c -p ~/media/pics/screen/
